file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Testing cypress package
  description: Some examples to test packages
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:3000
paths:
  /users:
    get:
      summary: Returns a list of users.
      description: A list of users
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A JSON array of user names
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  users:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        name:
                          type: string
                        age:
                          type: number
                      required:
                        - name
                        - age
              examples:
                OK:
                  value:
                    users:
                      - name: Luke
                        age: 31
                      - name: Han
                        age: 40
                      - name: Chewy
                        age: 50
                EMPTY:
                  value:
                    users: []
  /cards:
    get:
      summary: Returns a list of cards.
      description: A list of cards
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: page
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A JSON array of card names
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  users:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        name:
                          type: string
                      required:
                        - name
              examples:
                OK:
                  value:
                    users:
                      - name: Queen
                      - name: King
                      - name: Joker
  /dogs:
    parameters:
      - schema:
          type: string
        name: Authorization
        in: header
        required: true
    get:
      summary: Returns a list of dogs.
      description: A list of great dogs
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A JSON array of dog names
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  users:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        name:
                          type: string
                      required:
                        - name
              examples:
                OK:
                  value:
                    users:
                      - name: Paco
